Room DB implementieren (siehe Tutorial)
Table Route
    Name
    Begin (time)
    End (time)
    GPX file (link to file)
    Duration (time)
    POIs (list)
    Waypoints (list)

Table Poi
  Coordinates
  Link to Photo on filesystem

Table Waypoints
  List of Coordinates

